data.description: Sweet Spot between Riverside and Porter, around the corner from fun neighborhood hangouts at both Greenwood and Rosebank. Enviable access to Cornelia Fort, Forrest Green, and Shelby Bottoms. Direct routes to Eastland, Ellington, and Gallatin.  Brick 2 bedroom home renovated in 2004. Water line replaced and gas meter present.  Build Options: R6 (One And Two Family) level lot, elevated above street level. HPR examples abound. Driveway leads to deep backyard. No HOA. Located in both Urban Design Overlay (2007) and Contextual Overlay (2018). Outside Historic Overlay.  Income Options: Rentometer shows average rent $1,839 and median $1,775. AirDNA suggests $191 daily rate with 63% occupancy. Needs new roof and other repairs. As-is sale for investment or development.
